  # --- device_status: local device vitals ---
  # Shows hostname, IP, WiFi, CPU temp, memory, disk, uptime, battery, PID.
  # No url needed -- gathers data from local system calls.
  # Battery reads from PiSugar (requires pisugar pip package on Pi).
